{
  "texts": [
    "Datasets serve not only as a foundation for training LLMs but also as benchmarks for evaluating their performance.",
    "Each stage of datasets' application is critical for ensuring that the models are practically effective in real-world medical settings.",
    "Looking forward, the continued expansion and refinement of these datasets will be essential.",
    "Future research should focus on enhancing dataset transparency and quality, addressing privacy concerns, and integrating multimodal data to enrich model training.",
    "The development of medical datasets is a dynamic and evolving field that holds the key to unlocking the full potential of LLMs in medicine."
  ]
}